data.description: Great home with ample space recent updates throughout this open concept layout with breathtaking views of the golf course and private access through the back yard to the Country Clubhouse, pool, and tennis courts. This home has a lot to look forward to. Lots of natural light and great flow throughout this four-bedroom two-story home with the master bedroom being downstairs accompanied by three full bathrooms and one powder bath. This home has fresh paint, new flooring, granite, hardware throughout and new stainless steel appliances among some of the updates. Two living areas, two dining areas, two-car garage, this home has it all, space, views, updates and location. Buyer must verify all info & measurements.
